This paper focuses on text understanding and applies comprehension models based on neural networks to a word prediction task requiring broader context. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the arXiv sub-categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE), and Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV).
